          leading role in India's missile and space programs, earning the
          title “Missile Man of India”.
        </p>

        <p>
          What truly sets him apart wasn’t power or position — it was humility.
          He connected with students, believed in education, and dedicated his
          life to inspiring young minds to dream big.
        </p>

